name: Rebel Reinforcements (V)
Lore: 'Rebels rely on hidden ''cells'' of undercover operatives. Striking from hidden bases, troops or starfighters can arrive in a battle zone at any time.',
Text: 'Once per game, if opponent has more cards with ability on table than you do, draw destiny and retrieve up to that number of Rebel characters and/or Rebel starships (may take one retrieved card into hand).',
